data.text:
Welcome to our hospital

Whiskers and Paws Animal Hospital is centrally located in Kenwood with convenient access to the I-71 corridor. Our mission is to practice transformative veterinary medicine, from the routine to the complex, with the utmost compassion while supporting the needs of both the patient and their family. Our vision is to provide compassionate veterinary care that is unmatched in excellence, patient experience, and clinical outcomes.

Surgery

You can have confidence that our veterinarians and staff will work hard to ensure each procedure is thorough, done with the utmost expertise, and is as stress-free as possible for both you and your pet.
